<% content_for :title do %>Advertising<% end %>
<% content_for :description do %>Paid Search Marketing for your Small Business. Take away the hassle of bidding on keywords with our tailored PPC Campaigns.<% end %>
<% content_for :keywords do %>Paid Search Marketing, Pay Per Click, PPC, PPC campign, Paid Search Campaign, Keyword, Search Terms, Adwords, Bing, Ad Account, Keyword Bidding, <% end %>

<div class='bgimg advertising-bgimg'>
  <div class='col-sm-8 col-md-push-3'>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 col-xs-12 col-sm-8 text-left bgimg-content">
        <h1 style="font-weight:600;"><br/><br/>Increase your<br/> site’s traffic with<br/> Pay Per Click</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row grey">
  <div class="section">
    <div class="col-xs-12 text-center margin-bottom-20">
      <h2>Advertising</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 text-left">
      <p>Pay-Per-Click (PPC) is one of the most popular forms of advertising online. On the more popular search engines
        your advert is displayed in various places including the top, sides or display banners – you only pay when someone
        clicks on these ads.</p>
      <p>Search advertising is extremely targeted, and when done right you can deliver instant and meaningful traffic.
        The keywords generated will mean your site only appears when people search for the words you select. The control
        is in your hands as you can decide specifically what you advertise, the times and place your ads show and also you
        control your daily budget.</p>
      <p>With experience in AdWords, Yahoo and Bing and managing both low to high end budgets, we’re confident on getting
        your site ranking and traffic at a high level. What’s more, for any new advertisers to Google AdWords you can
        get a free advertising voucher worth £75 to kick start your PPC journey.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="section" style="width:100%;">
    <div class="col-xs-12 text-center margin-bottom-50">
      <h2>Conversion Tracking</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-6 text-right">
      <div class="left-text">
        <h3>You'll fundamentally want to measure the results of your PPC activities, and we'll set you up with conversion
          tracking tools such as Google analytics, so you can truly measure your ROI.</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-6">
      <%= image_tag 'hero.jpg', class: 'border-img-1' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="section grey">
    <div class="col-xs-12 text-center margin-bottom-50">
      <h2>Bespoke Marketing Services</h2>
      <h3>Here are some of the areas we can help with:</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
      <%= link_to website_path, class: 'service-link' do %>
          <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
            <%= image_tag 'icon-advertising-adwords.png', class: "margin-top-bottom-20" %>
            <h4 class="service-heading">Google AdWords</h4>
            <p>Our expertise in this area is second to none, and we’ll spend time finding the right formula for your business</p>
          </div>
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to seo_path, class: 'service-link' do %>
          <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
            <%= image_tag 'icon-advertising-bing.png', class: "margin-top-bottom-20" %>
            <h4 class="service-heading">Bing Ads</h4>
            <p>Make the most of Bing’s popular search engine with expertly placed ads</p>
          </div>
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to advertising_path, class: 'service-link' do %>
          <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
            <%= image_tag 'icon-advertising-ads.png', class: "margin-top-bottom-20" %>
            <h4 class="service-heading">Display Advertising</h4>
            <p>Your display ads will be targeting an audience that has already indicated an interest in your service or product</p>
          </div>
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to social_path, class: 'service-link' do %>
          <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
            <%= image_tag 'icon-advertising-sway.png', class: "margin-top-bottom-20" %>
            <h4 class="service-heading">Remarketing</h4>
            <p>Improve ROI and increase conversions by marketing to people who have all ready visited your website</p>
          </div>
      <% end %>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="section" style="width:100%;">
    <div class="col-xs-12 text-center margin-bottom-50">
      <h2>PPC</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-6 text-right">
      <div class="left-text">
        <h3 class="margin-bottom-50">PPC advertising through social media &lt;hyperlink to social media page&gt; including Facebook and LinkedIn
          are additional useful for start-ups and SMEs. By looking at estimated search traffic in a specific geographical
          location and estimated average cost per click.</h3>
        <div class="text-left"><%= submit_tag 'Get in touch', class: "btn-style" %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-6">
      <%= image_tag 'hero.jpg', class: 'border-img-1' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row green">
  <div class="section" style="width:100%;">
    <div class="col-md-12 text-center margin-bottom-50">
      <h2>Additional Services</h2>
    </div>

    <%= render partial: "page_links", locals: {service: @service} %>
  </div>
</div>